info.name: Digimon Tamers Tumblr Dashboard Icons
info.description: New post icons of some of the human characters from Digimon Tamers. Credit to rainbowdrusy.tumblr.com!!~ Don't worry about it looking like the text isn't there. It will show up once you install the icons. :)
info.additionalInfo: Gifs used are from http://giffactory.joeyteel.com/mug/tamers.html. In the set are: Takato, Rika, Henry, Kazu, Kenta, Ryo and Yamaki
